description:
You will be taken by the unique features of this unit. As you come through the private entrance, something rarely found in any Upper East Side building, you come in to soaring 20 foot high ceiling open space. This one bedroom home truly has the essence of a downtown loft, and not only will you enjoy 960 square feet of living space, 2 full bathrooms, a full size washer/dryer, custom designed kitchen w/ breakfast bar, and an over-sized living/dining area, but you will have a quaint private outdoor space and a functioning, wood burning fireplace - these are coveted features in any city apartment. Here, you are steps to the 4/5/6 trains, and the Q, with cross-town bus service just outside your door. This is truly a superb value.
Neighborhood Description;
This part of town is two and three express stops from the hustle and bustle of Union Square and Tribeca, respectively. However you can retreat to your peaceful and charming street after a day/night out. Fairway has everything you need to make a gourmet meal, and soon Whole Foods will come to help you impress your dinner guests. Steps away from Central Park, and equidistant to the Mayor's mansion (Carl Schurz Park) that overlooks the East River. no pets please

Welcome to The Townhouse @ 220 W 79, the Upper West Side's newest quintessential townhome development. Combining timeless pre-war charm with modern luxury, this 1900 built landmark townhome, situated within the Upper West Side-Central Park West Historic District, was gut renovated down to its shell in 2018.

Remarkably transformed into four full floor luxury rental residences, The Townhouse @ 220 W 79 redefines traditional thinking when it comes to townhome rental living. From offering virtual doorman and full time super accessibility, pin drop quietness and condo level finishes that perfect the blend of modern and historic, residents may truly appreciate how tranquil a retreat from the hustle and bustle of the city outside can be while making their home in a piece of history.

The third floor residence extends the full floor, proffering two bedrooms, one and a half baths and expansive rooms sizes. 

Apartment Features:
- Central heating/air; 
- In unit washer and vented dryer;
- Custom grey stained hardwood flooring
- Two decorative brick fireplaces;
- Virtual doorman;
- Full time super

Kitchen Features: 
- Bertazzoni range + microwave;
- Bosch dishwasher;
- Built in water filtration;
- Garbage disposal;
- Custom European cabinetry
